        </li>
        <li id="details-1" class="details">
          <div class="admo-tv">
            <%= image_tag("apps/gif-large.png") %>
          </div>
          <div class="description">
            <h2 class="catalog">Four structure menu</h2>
            <p>
              The four structure menu allows you to present your users with a selection of content and a follow up screen for each item containing further information or instructions.
